---
model: googleai/gemini-2.0-flash
input:
  schema:
    images: string[], Array of image URLs to analyze
    question?: string, Optional question about the images
    audioUrl?: string, Optional audio URL to transcribe
---

{{! Multimodal prompt demonstrating the media helper }}

{{role "user"}}
Please analyze the following content:

{{! Include multiple images using the media helper }}
{{#each images}}
{{media url=this}}
{{/each}}

{{! Optionally include audio }}
{{#if audioUrl}}
Also transcribe this audio:
{{media url=audioUrl}}
{{/if}}

{{#if question}}
Specific question: {{question}}
{{else}}
Describe what you see in detail.
{{/if}}

{{role "model"}}
I'll analyze the provided media content carefully.
